Liber Web Framework
=============================

This is simple MVC based PHP framework.


How to install
-----------------------------

1. Download the compressed file from http://github.com/djalmaoliveira/Liber/tarball/master;
2. Unpack on folder with public http access using `tar -pvxf file.tar.gz`, to preserve original permissions;
3. Open your web browser on folder above and go to 'manual/';


Examples
------------------------------
	You will find some examples in 'examples/' folder or 'manual/' folder.



